{"type": "article", "id": 28587, "title": "可以听音乐的太阳眼镜", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-23T06:51:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 75, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703121538tbFZDoKqwcUJNmpW.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>太阳眼镜和耳机二合一会怎样？初创公司 Zungle 最近就推出了一款特别的太阳眼镜 Zungle Panther，它通过骨传导音响系统让你可以一边进行户外运动一边听音乐或者进行通话。戴上后骨传导的麦克风会置于太阳穴附近，声波通过头骨传导到内耳，既不会被他人听到，也不会影响你听到外界的其它声音。通过蓝牙与手机进行配对之后，轻按控制键就能切换曲目或是接听电话。不同于其他智能眼镜，Zungle Panther 的造型要时髦不少，而且仅重 45 克，甚至要低于普通的太阳眼镜。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/zungle/zungle-wear-the-beats/\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 109 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031215365yeOgFxTLVDAfXQq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.61124694\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121536ndUK41BRcquAlMSo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09852941\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121537L8fXUwOnxcWEV7qR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54400978\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121537g03i5RKYL4wlxDjU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}